Assignment3

第三题：使用sklearn的AgglomerativeClustering完成层次聚类¶

实验内容：

  1. 使用sklearn的AgglomerativeClustering完成两个数据集的层次聚类
  2. 计算外部指标FMI和NMI
  3. 对6种形式的聚类效果可视化

注意：在运行本notebook前需要讲sklearn更新至0.20及以上版本

1. 导入模块¶

In [1]:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib inline

import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')

2. 生成数据集¶

In [2]:
from sklearn import datasets
X1, y1 = datasets.make_circles(n_samples = 1500, factor = 0.5, noise = 0.05, random_state = 32)
X2, y2 = datasets.make_moons(n_samples = 1500, noise = 0.05, random_state = 32)
In [3]:
colors = np.array(['#377eb8', '#ff7f00', '#4daf4a', '#f781bf', '#a65628', '#984ea3', '#999999', '#e41a1c', '#dede00'])
In [4]:
plt.title('dataset1')
plt.scatter(X1[:, 0], X1[:, 1], s = 10, c = colors[y1])
Out[4]:
<matplotlib.collections.PathCollection at 0x7f83310de040>
In [5]:
plt.title('dataset2')
plt.scatter(X2[:, 0], X2[:, 1], s = 10, c = colors[y2])
Out[5]:
<matplotlib.collections.PathCollection at 0x7f832de8ad60>

3. 导入模型¶

In [6]:
from sklearn.cluster import AgglomerativeClustering

4. 聚类¶

层次聚类的linkage参数表示我们要用哪种距离（最小、最大、平均）进行聚类。这里我们选择single，表示最小距离。complete表示最大距离，average表示平均距离。

注意：single参数是在sklearn 0.20版本才加入的！

In [7]:
model = AgglomerativeClustering(n_clusters = 2, linkage="single")
model.fit(X1)
Out[7]:
AgglomerativeClustering(linkage='single')

对于层次聚类算法，我们可以使用labels_属性获得聚类结果

5. 聚类效果可视化¶

In [8]:
pred = model.labels_
plt.title('dataset1')
plt.scatter(X1[:, 0], X1[:, 1], s = 10, color = colors[pred])
Out[8]:
<matplotlib.collections.PathCollection at 0x7f8327afc280>

Test¶

请你完成"single"，"complete"和"average"三种距离在两个数据集上的聚类任务，并绘制出聚类结果，计算6种情况的FMI和NMI

双击此处填写¶

1. 数据集1¶

距离度量方式 FMI NMI

In [31]:
# YOUR CODE HERE
from sklearn.cluster import AgglomerativeClustering
from sklearn.metrics import normalized_mutual_info_score
from sklearn.metrics import fowlkes_mallows_score

dataset1_nmi = []
dataset1_fmi = []
dataset2_nmi = []
dataset2_fmi = []

linkages = ["single", "complete", "average"]

plt.figure(figsize=(15,5))
for i in range(3):
    model = AgglomerativeClustering(n_clusters=2, linkage=linkages[i])
    model.fit(X1)
    dataset1_nmi.append(normalized_mutual_info_score(y1, model.labels_))
    dataset1_fmi.append(fowlkes_mallows_score(y1, model.labels_))
    plt.subplot(1,3,i+1)
    plt.title('dataset1:' + linkages[i])
    plt.scatter(X1[:, 0], X1[:, 1], s = 10, c = colors[model.labels_])
    
plt.show()
print("数据集1 NMI:",dataset1_nmi)
print("数据集1 FMI:",dataset1_fmi)

plt.figure(figsize=(15,5))
for i in range(3):
    model = AgglomerativeClustering(n_clusters=2, linkage=linkages[i])
    model.fit(X2)
    dataset2_nmi.append(normalized_mutual_info_score(y2, model.labels_))
    dataset2_fmi.append(fowlkes_mallows_score(y2, model.labels_))
    plt.subplot(1,3,i+1)
    plt.title('dataset2:' + linkages[i])
    plt.scatter(X2[:, 0], X2[:, 1], s = 10, c = colors[model.labels_])
   
plt.show()
print("数据集2 NMI:",dataset2_nmi)
print("数据集2 FMI:",dataset2_fmi)
